&lt;p&gt;The development hereby permitted shall only be carried out and completed strictly in accordance with the submitted plans hereby approved and any subsequent approval of details.
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the development hereby permitted is carried out in full accordance with the plans hereby approved.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Detailed drawings/full particulars of the proposed development showing the matters set out below must be submitted to and approved by the Local Planning Authority, in writing, before any work on the relevant area is commenced. The development shall not be carried out otherwise than in accordance with the details thus approved.
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
a) The proposed front boundary treatment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;b) The proposed planting within the front forecourt.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
REASON: In order to preserve the character and appearance of the host building and the Graham Road and Mapledene Conservation Area as well as provide appropriate compensatory measures for the loss of the existing tree.&lt;/p&gt;
